T*
(  - macOS first) Tj
T*
(  - Windows second) Tj
T*
(  - Linux package third) Tj
T*
(Step 0.4: Finalize minimum UX requirements for non-technical users.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Deliverable:) Tj
T*
(- Written acceptance criteria for "one-click ready".) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
