T*
(--------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
(Goal: Move lifecycle control to one persistent local service.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Step 1.1: Create NodeSupervisor module \(single owner of child processes\).) Tj
T*
(  - Start/stop/restart full/miner/wallet.) Tj
T*
